727590f-b.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 127th Place
727590f-b.text:
Northern Boulevard, east from 127th Place toward the
Flushing River bridge. View 2 is east from near Willets
Point Boulevard.
P. L. Sperr  October 5, 1935
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
